{"tid":1646784,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"疑有職員洩露示威者資料　 渣打：嚴肅跟進，強調絕不姑息","createTime":"2019-10-11T12:44:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T05:03:05.000Z","uid":66271,"like":153,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"007751850e8ecd700eba88089629703a619152a1","tid":1646784,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:44:04.000Z","msg":"網上傳言稱，一名在青衣城渣打銀行分行任職的女職員利用職權及盜用同事員工帳號，登入銀行系統調查客戶資料，並交予任職警察的丈夫。傳言指，該名職員在兩個月內，最少交了9名示威者資料予其丈夫，其中有人被捕。<br />\n渣打銀行今早在社交網站回應稱，注意到相關言論，公司正嚴肅跟進事件，若發現任何違規行為，絕不姑息。<br />\n<br />\n渣打銀行就此事件在社交網站貼文回應稱，公司一向十分重視客戶私隱，有嚴謹機制保障客戶資料。由於指控嚴重，渣打銀行正嚴肅跟進，若發現任何違規行為，絕不姑息"},{"pid":"45d311d6fae2ca384ef69221af571ab81312b4fd","tid":1646784,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:45:11.000Z","msg":"突發！香城online現已公開發售！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1646714\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1646714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d1f42b7d453d78a3fa20c79ca047d2aeda9de04d","tid":1646784,"uid":66049,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652eb0009596064e6cb012c79e30b6847ec61469","tid":1646784,"uid":55533,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T13:09:45.000Z","msg":"炒左佢啦"},{"pid":"db26033e1a695d995849477b3fe1162f4e786959","tid":1646784,"uid":31773,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T13:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />算渣打兜得快"},{"pid":"977ac91e0179932446c95923a11492c23ebbf566","tid":1646784,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T13:18:13.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"59f04ac2836314e1daa9157272e99e1f31b8f9a1","tid":1646784,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c