46784,"uid":167394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7241158a50afe3e379cffcbd72ecb01064d5c89","tid":1646784,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:08:47.000Z","msg":"另一個POST好似話內部掉左去第個位<br />\n未知會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T01:07:22.000Z","msg":"所以要找人報俾歐盟聽"},{"pid":"ec7e04d63f0ef9f9104f91cef544b1e03145a071","tid":1646784,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:00:21.000Z","msg":"渣打自己諗喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09b8d9d2aa0de61db6238e8fe93305bf3e58db17","tid":1646784,"uid":73092,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:11:01.000Z","msg":"警嫂Bonnie Tong 唐曉華濫用公司客戶資料，侵犯客戶個人私隱，將手足個人資料起底，交比做警嘅老公<br />\n<br />\n呢個終極藍絲大話精，公司問佢死口唔認，仲話比人盗用facebook，大家睇佢FB專like藍C，仲話為中國喝彩<br />\n<br />\n佢末調去青衣城之前係奥海城分行，原來佢係奥海城分行用同事staff ID 幫佢popo老公透過銀行系統起手足個人資料，佢協助警方拉人，估計起左8-10人，件事揚左，據了解成間奧海城分行人人自危，比佢害死，最惨有人唔知佢用同事staff ID<br />\n<br />\n佢係831之後開會期間同同事大讚警方係太子表現,，拉曬暴徒，令好多同事不滿<br />\n<br />\n據知Bonnie Tong 已經被禁落分行，只可坐係寫字樓，加上有客人投訴，又怕分行被裝修，但又怕炒佢得罪藍屍，所以渣打同佢上司會保佢，直至淡化事件為止<br />\n<br />\n更新：自從831後佢係奥海城分行最少用4位同事staff login 查客戶資料，包括一位離職同事，據了解該離職同事因為知道佢惡行，因害怕被追究，所以離職。加上佢最少2次開早會期間稱呼示威者做（死曱甴）,希望警察老公殺死曱甴<br />\n<br />\n佢經已交左手足資料比做警嘅老公，亦都唔知交左幾多比警，渣打銀行CEMS系統可以用名去check客戶資料，所以有手足擔心可以取消户口信用咭<br />\n<br />\n佢同前上司現任SME 老闆Anthony 有路，公司旅行期間曾一齊同房，平時番工時聲稱見客，實情去尖沙咀皇家太平洋洒店火爆房，據聞Bonnie 老公知情<br />\n<br />\n今日起公司已停佢職，Bonnie 上司Joe Tai已經講左1-2個月後復，同出面講比人盗用facebook account password，件事調淡就冇事<br />\n仆街 #賤人 #渣打<br />\n香港仆街逐個捉<br />\n請訂閱支持仆街集中營🗿<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/PoorGuyCamp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FPoorGuyCamp&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcsyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=239e8902\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/PoorGuyCamp</a>"},{"pid":"bd790dceac25776deb9eaf098f1bd1455f07dcc6","tid":1646784,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db26033e1a695d995849477b3fe1162f4e786959","tid":1646784,"uid":31773,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T13:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />算渣打兜得快"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:17:26.000Z","msg":"渣兜銀行嘛"},{"pid":"3311c8c5dbdafc5f9beaa245aed75650bd50e7a7","tid":1646784,"uid":60868,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:21:48.000Z","msg":"呢d已經係好嚴重違反左code of conduct<br />\n銀行根本係要即炒+控告，邊有得保？"},{"pid":"418ce04e1ca8f5937139ab99890232e20bdb7cbf","tid":1646784,"uid":94836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:15:19.000Z","msg":"可以點搞大"},{"pid":"afe53ba78f44723c36eba9f5904624b1048a3032","tid":1646784,"uid":85168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2415e6c6ae6459d46ffb7172ef13f3f8c562117a","tid":1646784,"uid":97389,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"5ba31a9c7645bbf2356477aa0821217468a71844","tid":1646784,"uid":258328,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T13:27:56.000Z","msg":"告去國際組織算啦<br />\n賠返百零億就無事"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T13:53:27.000Z","msg":"告去GDPR.<br />\n賠死渣打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵歐盟國家護照持有者告上去就得.<br />\n銀行唔會唔知客戶私隱有幾緊要, 連港共依家都未敢出手搞呢樣嘢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:45:33.000Z","msg":"係咪一定要當事人先得？"},{"pid":"4e6275307598c4d1719ba59ee02f49197690527d","tid":1646784,"uid":279981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:52:36.000Z","msg":"留返同歐盟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ab3f864a3d3601